  &lt;p id="6evpLK"&gt;VidCon &lt;a href="https://www.vidcon.com/info/fz5mw5/covid-19-statement"&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; that its US convention, &lt;a href="https://variety.com/2021/digital/news/vidcon-2021-dates-featured-creators-announced-for-return-to-anaheim-convention-center-1234934765/"&gt;scheduled in late October&lt;/a&gt;, has been canceled due to concerns over the increasing number of COVID cases. The organizers, however, say that VidCon 2022 is scheduled for June 22nd-25th and that non single-day tickets for the 2021 event will automatically transfer to the new event. VidCon has noted, though, that the event next year won’t necessarily have the same guests and activities planned for this year.&lt;/p&gt;
